<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:16:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>碧桂园律师告诉法庭，预计二月份与债权人达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-expects-reach-terms-with-creditors-february-lawyer-tells-court-2025-01-20/</link><description>中国房地产公司碧桂园的律师周一对香港一家法院表示，该公司已拖欠债务偿还义务，预计下个月将与债权人达成满意的条款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 02:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-expects-reach-terms-with-creditors-february-lawyer-tells-court-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>东盟维持禁止缅甸将军参加峰会的决定，敦促在南海保持克制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-upholds-decision-bar-myanmar-generals-summits-urges-self-restraint-s-china-2025-01-20/</link><description>现任轮值主席国马来西亚周一表示，东南亚集团东盟各国外长在周末务虚会上维持了禁止缅甸执政将军参加峰会并将缅甸的参与限制在非政治层面的决定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:41:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-upholds-decision-bar-myanmar-generals-summits-urges-self-restraint-s-china-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>随着特朗普第二任期的到来，美元走强，股市走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-20/</link><description>美元坚挺，周一亚洲股市谨慎乐观，因投资者等待唐纳德·特朗普就任第二任总统的头几个小时内预期将发布的一系列政策公告，并关注日本在本周末加息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:17:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国维持基准贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-2025-01-20/</link><description>正如预期的那样，中国连续第三个月维持基准贷款利率不变，因为人民币贬值限制了北京的货币政策宽松力度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>美国 TikTok 爱好者如释重负，希望随着应用程序的恢复，“魔法”回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/relieved-us-tiktok-enthusiasts-hope-magic-returns-app-is-restored-2025-01-20/</link><description>尽管人们对 TikTok 的未来仍存在疑问，但一些用户感叹他们对政府的信任将永远不会像以前一样。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 00:15:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/relieved-us-tiktok-enthusiasts-hope-magic-returns-app-is-restored-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国老龄化村庄在脆弱的经济中面临巨大的医疗缺口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ageing-villages-face-yawning-healthcare-gap-fragile-economy-2025-01-19/</link><description>中国的发展模式正处于十字路口，要么是大幅提高养老金和医疗支出，要么是产业升级和城镇化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 23:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ageing-villages-face-yawning-healthcare-gap-fragile-economy-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国当选副总统万斯在就职前会见中国外长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-vp-elect-vance-meets-with-chinese-counterpart-ahead-inauguration-2025-01-19/</link><description>美国当选副总统万斯周日会见了中国国家副主席韩正，一天后他和当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将宣誓就职。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 19:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-vp-elect-vance-meets-with-chinese-counterpart-ahead-inauguration-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普安全顾问不排除中国继续拥有 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-security-adviser-doesnt-rule-out-continued-chinese-ownership-tiktok-2025-01-19/</link><description>Mike Waltzs 表示用户数据必须受到保护并存储在美国</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 14:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-security-adviser-doesnt-rule-out-continued-chinese-ownership-tiktok-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 正在恢复服务，感谢特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-goes-dark-us-users-trump-says-save-tiktok-2025-01-19/</link><description>即使是暂时的，TikTok 前所未有的关闭也必将对中美关系、美国政治、社交媒体市场和数百万美国人产生广泛影响。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 13:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-goes-dark-us-users-trump-says-save-tiktok-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国公布到2035年建设“教育强国”的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-unveils-2024-2035-plan-build-strong-education-nation-2025-01-19/</link><description>中国发布了第一个到2035年建设“教育强国”的国家行动计划，称该计划将有助于协调教育发展，提高创新效率，建设“强国”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 11:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-unveils-2024-2035-plan-build-strong-education-nation-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与美国在南海举行联合海上演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-hold-joint-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2025-01-19/</link><description>马尼拉武装部队周日表示，菲律宾和美国第五次在南海举行联合海上演习，此举可能会激怒中国。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 05:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-hold-joint-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 停止为美国用户服务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-stops-working-us-users-2025-01-19/</link><description>周六，在联邦对这款中国短视频应用程序的禁令生效之前，TikTok 在美国关闭，切断了对这个吸引近一半美国人、推动小企业发展并塑造网络文化的平台的访问。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 03:54:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-stops-working-us-users-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 告诉用户周日将在美国“暂时无法使用”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-tells-users-it-will-be-temporarily-unavailable-us-sunday-2025-01-19/</link><description>周六晚些时候，TikTok 告诉美国用户，周日禁止该应用程序的法律在美国生效后，该应用程序将“暂时无法使用”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 02:19:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-tells-users-it-will-be-temporarily-unavailable-us-sunday-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>据 The Information 报道，甲骨文准备从格林尼治标准时间 0200 开始关闭 TikTok 服务器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/oracle-prepares-start-shutting-tiktok-servers-0200-gmt-information-reports-2025-01-19/</link><description>TikTok 美国业务的主要云计算提供商甲骨文的领导者已告诉部分员工，准备在美国东部时间周六晚上 9 点（格林威治标准时间周日 0200 点）关闭托管美国 TikTok 数据的服务器，赶在美国法律禁止之前据《The Information》报道，该应用程序从周日开始使用。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 02:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/oracle-prepares-start-shutting-tiktok-servers-0200-gmt-information-reports-2025-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>《华尔街日报》报道，特朗普希望以总统身份访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-wants-visit-china-president-wsj-reports-2025-01-18/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周六援引知情人士的话报道，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普告诉顾问，他希望在就职后前往中国。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 22:54:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-wants-visit-china-president-wsj-reports-2025-01-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>